                        <div class="pe_right">
                            <a href="http://www.cio.com.cn/eyan/view/22695" class="ti">颜色及标记符号管理</a>
                            <div style="dispaly:block" class="ti_p"><p class="ti_p">颜色及标记符号管理 : 1）将信息符号化，便于速记2）付上符号解说表，熟记符号的意义3）红线标记重点，快速理解笔记内容4）善用线条与箭头，标示对象关系或阅读动线5）练习简单图解，将复杂信息化为图像6）排列色彩序阶，标示重点7）三色法：赋予颜色意义，协助信息分类8）选用3-5个颜色，避免色彩过多，混淆重点9）红笔：...<br /><span class="zk" style="color:blue;" >展开&gt;&gt; </span></p></div>
                            <div style="display:none" class="ti_p"><p  class="ti_p"><p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">颜色及标记符号管理</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"> </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">:</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"> </span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.85pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">1</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）将信息符号化，便于速记</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.85pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">2</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）付上符号解说表，熟记符号的意义</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.85pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">3</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）红线标记重点，快速理解笔记内容</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.85pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">4</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）善用线条与箭头，标示对象关系或阅读动线</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"><span></span><span></span><span></span>5</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）练习简单图解，将复杂信息化为图像</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p>
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"><span></span><span></span><span></span>6</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）排列色彩序阶，标示重点</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">7</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）三色法：赋予颜色意义，协助信息分类</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">8</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）选用</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">3-5</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">个颜色，避免色彩过多，混淆重点</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">9</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）红笔：抄写段落标题，作为笔记大纲</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">10</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）荧光笔</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">/</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">色铅笔：区分色块，进行可视化管理</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">11</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）各色便利贴：进行颜色管理</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
</p><br />
<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;">12</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:SimSun;">）贴纸与印章：增添色彩与趣味</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:新細明體;"></span>
